 * that then displays the current temperature and desired temperature on a LCD display.
 *  
 * Pin layout used:
 * -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 *             MFRC522                    ESP8266       
 *             Reader/PCD                 
 * Signal      Pin                        Pin           
 * -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 * RST/Reset   RST                        D3        
 * SPI SS      SDA(SS)                    D8        
 * SPI MOSI    MOSI                       D7       
 * SPI MISO    MISO                       D6      
 * SPI SCK     SCK                        D5       
 *
 * 
 */


